{"tid":1720993,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一分鐘學化學： CS 分子話你知","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:43:04.000Z","uid":96182,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca5356c6b0813d063011dff2250be75d47aa061","tid":1720993,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/一分鐘學化學-cs-分子話你知\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%AD%B8%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%B8-cs-%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVczcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=6c5747a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%AD%B8%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%B8-cs-%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5&h=33741e68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/一分鐘學化學-cs-分子話你知</a><br />\n係悶啲，但理科、文科、呀...... 都明到。<br />\n<br />\nCS 分子有 4 部分：<br />\n<br />\nCl, Chlorine 氯<br />\nBenzene ring 苯環 <br />\nC=C 碳雙鍵<br />\nCN 山埃<br />\n1-3 都冇乜極性，所以 CS 唔溶係水，好難落雨沖走！（水有極性，所以極性部分多嘅分子先溶係水）。<br />\n<br />\n25℃ 嘅一堆 CS 固體相對冇咁大鑊，但如果係微粒狀入眼鼻口你就 HiHi 。<br />\n<br />\n有 1 及 4 燃燒就可出 hydrogen chloride, HCl 氣（吸多會肺水腫）同 hydrogen cyanide, HCN 氣（山埃氣：死得）。<br />\n<br />\n有 2 苯環就冇乜好嘢，入咗身體經肝生成苯 benzene ，致癌例如血癌。<br />\n<br />\n有 3 就代表比較易分解。可以用碱性水解分解 CS 成冇咁催淚嘅產物。<br />\n<br />\n有 1+2 就代表燃燒可產生二噁英 (dioxins) ，有 1+2 亦代表好穩定， dioxins 亦有 1+2 ，所以可以係大自然殘留幾十年！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/74882983_10157575952717158_6708554499046244352_o_Fgz2u_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F74882983_10157575952717158_6708554499046244352_o_Fgz2u_1200x0.jpg&h=bbebb04c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e09af1254b229fb12d1bac295eefde52904cff67","tid":1720993,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"024b7072c120fe2ba489527f3196b049fca75c1f","tid":1720993,"uid":168567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:02:17.000Z","msg":"毅進無chem 讀"},{"pid":"b0fd237b9f4ee128b852dc232bb9cb9865caf2a7","tid":1720993,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"814e37ba451bfdaad8f65d5e9ee264d34e5de72d","tid":1720993,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1103da3660e83afba1b381c8de9553d358a79bf3","tid":1720993,"uid":227449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"2,3,7,8-tetrachlorodibenzo-p-dioxin<br />\n依隻先最毒 完全無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入咗身體一世都排唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}